                                <abbr>Prof.</abbr>
                                <expan>Professor</expan>
                            </choice> Kunth</addrLine>
                        <addrLine>mit 3 Büchern <lb/>
                            <choice>
                                <abbr>u</abbr>
                                <expan>und</expan>
                            </choice> noch einem</addrLine>
                        <addrLine>Briefe. </addrLine>
